# Khargana, Selenginsky District, Republic of Buryatia

}}
Khargana () is a rural locality (an ulus) in Selenginsky District, Republic of Buryatia, Russia. The population was 950 as of 2010. There are 42 streets.
Geography
Khargana is located 36&nbsp;km northeast of Gusinoozyorsk (the district's administrative centre) by road. Nizhny Ubukun is the nearest rural locality.
